  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753520/extras/65d4882e50d7152e2c4f30385b6c77df.avif?t=1721668481\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>We've all been there. You drank too much before bed, and now you've woken up in the middle of the night with the urge. <br><br>The goal is simple. Get to the bathroom before you pee your pants. <br><br>It's just a simple game about not peeing your pants. <br><br>Sometimes, that's harder than it seems.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753520/extras/42fbd998fc4e458aa65e4fb5730fc81a.poster.avif?t=1721668481\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753520/extras/42fbd998fc4e458aa65e4fb5730fc81a.webm?t=1721668481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2753520/extras/42fbd998fc4e458aa65e4fb5730fc81a.mp4?t=1721668481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Features: <br><br>Riveting Storyline<br>Explorationg<br>A testament to self control.<br><br>You'll adventure through an atmospheric home, trying to find your way to your ultimate goal. The Bathroom. <br>You'll have to use your wits to solve puzzles, explore new areas, and try to survive. <br><br>With an advanced scared system that forces you to stay on your toes by pressing buttons as they appear.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Check out our new project. All the fun without the bladder control.</h2>",
